Mission:
STUDIO-001

Title:
CEO Workflow

Goal:
Eliminate the developer workflow for the CEO. Atlas Studio becomes the operational interface for intent through release.

Focus:
CEO Workflow screen in Atlas Studio
Dev API pipeline for decision, audit, and git release
Intent → Branch Director Decision → Execution → Review → CEO Approval → Publish
Git operations encapsulated behind Atlas services

Constraints:
No breaking changes to CLI workflows — terminal remains for development and recovery
CEO must explicitly approve before publish
.env files must never be staged or committed

Success:
CEO can build, review, and release an initiative entirely from Atlas Studio at /studio/ceo-workflow.
No manual git, npm, or audit commands required for normal operations.
